<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Security alert: email change requested — Mishka Den</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px; color: #222;">
    <h1 style="font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 16px;">Email change requested, {{ display_name }}</h1>
    <p>Someone (probably you) just requested to change the email address on your Mishka Den account. The new address (<strong>{{ new_email_masked }}</strong>) has been sent a confirmation link.</p>
    <p><strong>If this was you</strong>, no action needed — just click the link in the new mailbox to finish.</p>
    <p><strong>If this was NOT you</strong>, your account may be compromised. We recommend:</p>
    <ol>
        <li>Sign in to Mishka Den and <a href="https://mishka.minified.work/me/password">change your password</a> immediately.</li>
        <li>The pending email-change link expires in 24 hours; if it's not clicked, your address stays as it is now.</li>
    </ol>
    <p style="margin-top: 32px; font-size: 13px; color: #888;">— Mishka, the den mother for your family</p>
</body>
